{"tid":440120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「阿嬌男朋友」醫界王陽明改做陰道美容","createTime":"2017-10-18T12:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T18:01:07.000Z","uid":78657,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2242c5b0d0fa7367cc1f266af4434f793f5f3e9","tid":440120,"uid":78657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20171017ent014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20171017ent014%2F&d=9BZZCRCLOdbvgYblKvxMCW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c2fc58d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20171017ent014/</a><br />\n<br />\n今年32歲的賴弘國，在陳怡蓉老公薛博仁所開設的聖緹雅醫美診所擔任「技術總監暨海外事業部長」，最近轉行做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「陰道美容」</span></span>。因為長得帥，放電能力超強，尤其頂著「醫界王陽明」的光環，帥氣外表備受注目，堪稱高富帥的代表。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得啦～～～ 明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白哂</span>"},{"pid":"0226dd5111fcc87deff1ee2f654197aa21085708","tid":440120,"uid":78657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2413cfd29ce8e15226e522346d90e180a6586cbb","tid":440120,"uid":140261,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐?"},{"pid":"b94ae6bf256cfe14d99a1dfd2c6ebc510b1c00ce","tid":440120,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67544cd0439a31766203d02698c3f051a2b55650","tid":440120,"uid":22104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"白哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /